msgstr "Esialgse .cvsignore-faili loomine aktiivses kataloogis"

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Kirjeldus"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> is used to create a preliminary "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> in the current directory. It does this based "
"on certain contents it finds in <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> loob aktiivses kataloogis esialgse "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename>-faili. Selle aluseks võetakse faili "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename> sisu."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No lines will be removed from any existing <filename>.cvsignore</filename>. "
"If there is not already a <filename>.cvsignore</filename> file, it will be "
"added to the cvs repository."
msgstr ""
"Ühestki senisest <filename>.cvsignore</filename>-failist ei eemaldata ühtegi "
"rida. Kui <filename>.cvsignore</filename>-faili veel ei ole, lisatakse see "
"CVS-hoidlasse."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must have a <filename>Makefile.am</filename> in the current "
"directory for this tool to work."
msgstr ""
"Arvesta, et selle tööriista kasutamiseks peab aktiivses kataloogis olema "
"<filename>Makefile.am</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr "See utiliit kuulub &kde; tarkvaraarenduse komplekti koosseisu."

